      "when_to_use": "When you have many features and need automated feature importance filtering, plus missing value imputation and risk table mapping. Used by teams like active_queueing_pfoc, active_queueing_mfnri that have 100+ features from variable catalogs and need data preprocessing.",
      "when_not_to_use": "If you don't have missing values or categorical risk features (use training_with_evaluation). If you need registration (use complete_e2e). If you only need feature selection without MVI/risk tables (use training_with_calibration_fs).",
